            "title": "積金評級：3月份強積金人均蝕2.13萬元 抹去2025年近半收益",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">積金評級今早發表最新報告，估計今年3月份強積金錄得約1022億元破紀錄的單月虧損，人均約蝕2.13萬元，抹去2025年全年收益近半。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報告指出，根據「積金評級所有基金表現指數」截至3月底時數字計算，強積金單月投資虧損約1022億元，錄得6.27%負回報，導致今年首季強積金轉蝕312億元，季度負回報1.98%，是2022年以來首次在年度首季錄得負回報，也令強積金成員今年以來人均由賺轉蝕6506元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850640-%e7%a9%8d%e9%87%91%e8%a9%95%e7%b4%9a%ef%bc%9a3%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e5%bc%b7%e7%a9%8d%e9%87%91%e4%ba%ba%e5%9d%87%e8%9d%952-13%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83-%e6%8a%b9%e5%8e%bb2025%e5%b9%b4%e8%bf%91%e5%8d%8a%e6%94%b6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250423_FI_source-web_MPF-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 10:40:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "標普恐快手今年自由現金流或減逾半 股價應聲受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">媒體引述標準普爾報告指，擔心快手(01024)今年自由現金流或減逾半；快手今早初段股價應聲受壓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至上午約10時18分，快手報45.1元，跌3.43%，成交已達9.96億元；稍早前該股最低曾見45元，跌3.64%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850549-%e6%a8%99%e6%99%ae%e6%81%90%e5%bf%ab%e6%89%8b%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e7%8f%be%e9%87%91%e6%b5%81%e6%88%96%e6%b8%9b%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e6%87%89%e8%81%b2%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93",
