        {
            "title": "長江辰芯入場費4028元  下周五掛牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">長春長江辰芯(03277)今起招股，招股價39.88元，每手100股，入場費4028.23元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1187x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260409_FI_03277_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1187x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260409_FI_03277_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">發售6529.42萬股H股，香港公開發售佔10%，其餘為國際配售。每股招股價39.88元，集資最多26.04億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">聯席保薦人為中信証券、國泰海通。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">股份將於4 月17日掛牌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資所得款項淨額約25.036億元。約55%，或13.77億元用於增加研發投資 ; 約21%，或5.258億元用於建立一個先進的CMOS圖像傳感器研發中心；約4%，或1億元用於擴展封裝及測試生產線；約10%，或2.504億元拓張海外運營；及約10%用於營運資金及一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850460-%e9%95%b7%e6%b1%9f%e8%be%b0%e8%8a%af%e5%85%a5%e5%a0%b4%e8%b2%bb4028%e5%85%83-%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%94%e6%8e%9b%e7%89%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/03277.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 10:02:35",
